    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i've heard some people say that higher wages are actually good for the local economy though, like they give people more money to spend back in the community. is there any actual data for that, or is it just a theory? most of the business stuff i read seems to disagree with it.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
